datafield.subfield:
00003 Distribution of ToAs for the combined data sets. The band centre frequencies ($
u$) are colour encoded as follows: black: $
u&lt;$~500~MHz, red: 500~MHz~$&lt;
u&lt;$~750~MHz, green: 750~MHz~$&lt;
u&lt;$~1000~MHz, blue: 1000~MHz~$&lt;
u&lt;$~1500~MHz, aqua: 1500~MHz~$&lt;
u&lt;$~2000~MHz and pink: 2000~MHz~$&lt;
u&lt;$~4000~MHz.
